medium.question:
What visual effect will this CSS gradient create?

```css
.banner {
  background: linear-gradient(45deg, 
    #ff6b6b 0%, 
    #4ecdc4 50%, 
    #45b7d1 100%
  );
}
```

What sizing will this CSS rem/em comparison create?

```css
html { font-size: 16px; }
.parent { font-size: 20px; }
.child-em { font-size: 1.5em; }
.child-rem { font-size: 1.5rem; }
```

```html
<div class='parent'>
  <span class='child-em'>EM Text</span>
  <span class='child-rem'>REM Text</span>
</div>
```

hard.question:
How will this box-sizing comparison affect element dimensions?

```css
.content-box {
  box-sizing: content-box;
  width: 200px;
  padding: 20px;
  border: 5px solid black;
}

.border-box {
  box-sizing: border-box;
  width: 200px;
  padding: 20px;
  border: 5px solid black;
}
```
